body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting us. My name is Kyle King and I'm with ABC Car Dealership. May I have your name please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hello Kyle, my name is Shirley Scott.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Shirley. Can you please provide me with your date of birth in the format day followed by month followed by year?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: My date of birth is two five zero three one nine seven zero.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Shirley. One last detail we need is your postal code. Could you please share that with me?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: My postal code is A two B nine G four.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for providing those details, Shirley. We value your privacy and aim to ensure your information is secure. Is there anything else we can assist you with?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I appreciate your concern, but I'm feeling disappointed about the privacy issue. Can you help resolve it?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Absolutely, Shirley. We will investigate this matter and ensure your information is handled securely. Thank you for bringing this to our attention. We will do our best to resolve the issue.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for your time, Shirley. If you require any further assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out to us. Have a great day! Goodbye.
